## Key Features & Technologies

### Key Features
- 5-minute micro-lessons that fit adult daily life
- Decodable reading paths: syllables → words → sentences
- Offline-first learning (works even with poor network)
- Cultural + language relevance (mother tongue first)
- Simple onboarding: zero digital literacy required

### Technologies
- Flutter mobile app (cross platform: Android & iOS)
- Local SQLite for offline user progress storage
- Cloud backend (Node.js/Firebase) for content + analytics
- REST API for lessons + progress sync
